sentences: Anne Manson (born 1961, Cambridge, Massachusetts) is an American orchestral and opera conductor.
Manson was music director of the Kansas City Symphony from 1999 until 2003, and is currently music director of the Manitoba Chamber Orchestra.

She was conductor of London's Mecklenburgh Opera from 1988 to 1996, then served as an assistant to Claudio Abbado.
